sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User / Data Scientist
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS 1.2+
    participant WebhookSrv as Webhook Server<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Controller as modelmesh-controller<br/>(Go Operator)
    participant ModelMesh as ModelMesh Sidecar<br/>8033/TCP gRPC
    participant etcd as etcd<br/>2379/TCP gRPC TLS
    participant Puller as Puller Sidecar<br/>8086/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Client as Inference Client
    participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant RESTProxy as REST Proxy<br/>HTTP
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>(Triton/OVMS/MLServer)

    rect rgb(220, 235, 255)
        Note over User,Storage: Flow 1: Model Registration (Predictor Creation)
        User->>K8sAPI: POST Predictor CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (Predictor)
        Controller->>ModelMesh: gRPC SetVModel<br/>TLS optional, mTLS optional
        ModelMesh->>etcd: Register model placement<br/>TLS optional, Username/Password
        ModelMesh->>Puller: Download model<br/>gRPC 8086/TCP (pod-local)
        Puller->>Storage: GET model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, Storage credentials
        Storage-->>Puller: Model artifacts
        Puller-->>ModelMesh: Model cached locally
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Update Predictor status<br/>ServiceAccount token
    end

    rect rgb(255, 235, 220)
        Note over Client,Runtime: Flow 2: Model Inference Request (RHOAI)
        Client->>OAuthProxy: HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS, OAuth token
        OAuthProxy->>RESTProxy: HTTP (pod-local)<br/>No encryption
        RESTProxy->>ModelMesh: gRPC/8033<br/>TLS optional
        ModelMesh->>etcd: Routing lookup<br/>TLS optional, Username/Password
        etcd-->>ModelMesh: Model location
        ModelMesh->>Runtime: Inference request<br/>Unix socket / gRPC (pod-local)
        Runtime-->>ModelMesh: Prediction result
        ModelMesh-->>RESTProxy: gRPC response
        RESTProxy-->>OAuthProxy: HTTP response
        OAuthProxy-->>Client: HTTPS response
    end

    rect rgb(220, 255, 220)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 3: ServingRuntime Deployment
        User->>K8sAPI: POST ServingRuntime CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>WebhookSrv: Validate SR spec<br/>HTTPS/9443, API server cert
        WebhookSrv-->>K8sAPI: Validation result
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event (ServingRuntime)
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>ServiceAccount token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create HPA<br/>ServiceAccount token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Copy etcd Secret<br/>ServiceAccount token
    end
